              Choosing an Executor
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/planning-tools/checklists/guardian" class="sidebar-link" style="font-family: Inter, -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #1a2e44; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: none; padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 6px; display: block; transition: background 0.2s;">
