          </h2>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4b5563; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">
            When someone dies, their executor must locate assets, notify relevant parties, and usually apply for probate. This comprehensive 99-item checklist covers immediate steps, gathering documents, financial accounts, death notifications, and the entire probate process.
          </p>
          <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: #c9a227; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;">
