          </h2>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4b5563; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">
            Should you use a DIY kit, online service, or solicitor? This 79-item checklist helps you evaluate your situation's complexity and compare the pros, cons, and costs of each option to make the right choice for your circumstances.
          </p>
          <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: #c9a227; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;">
