          </h2>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4b5563; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">
            Your executor handles everything after you die. This 51-item checklist covers essential qualities, practical considerations, potential conflicts, co-executor options, questions to discuss with your chosen person, and red flags to watch for.
          </p>
          <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: #c9a227; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;">
