            Choosing a Guardian Checklist
          </h2>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4b5563; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">
            If you have children under 18, choosing who would raise them is critical. This 70-item checklist explores essential qualities, practical considerations, values alignment, relationship factors, special needs considerations, and difficult situations to think through.
          </p>
          <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: #c9a227; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;">
            <span>Start Checklist</span>
            <span>‚Üí</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- Checklist 5: Preparation for Making a Will -->
    <a href="/planning-tools/checklists/preparation" style="display: block; background: white; border: 2px solid #e5e2dd; border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease;">
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 24px;">
        <div style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 60px; height: 60px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2e44 0%, #2a4560 100%); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 28px;">
          üìù
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1;">
          <h2 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2e44; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">
            Preparation for Making a Will Checklist
          </h2>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4b5563; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">
            Before you create your will, gather essential information. This 53-item checklist covers your personal details, family situation, beneficiaries, executor and guardian choices, specific gifts, special instructions, and documents to have ready.
          </p>
          <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: #c9a227; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;">
