          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4b5563; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">
            Get a clear picture of what you own. This 66-item checklist covers property, money and banking, superannuation, investments, vehicles, valuables, household contents, digital assets, business assets, and debts. Estimates are fine for most items.
          </p>
